A Message to the White Hand
Planted a Rohirric banner over a slain Uruk ([placeholder]/[placeholder])

Rohirric banners planted upon the bodies of the Uruk-hai you've slain should send a strong message to the foes coming down from Isengard.\n\nYou should defeat several Uruks and plant banners upon them where they fall.
Uruks can be found at the Fords of Isen in the western Westfold.\n\nYou should plant banners in the bodies of Uruks you've killed.
You have defeated a number of Uruks at the Fords of Isen, and claimed their deaths with proud banners of the Rohirrim.\n\nThe Fords will not be safe for foes while Rohan endures.
